First Department,

May, 1975

(May 1, 1975) In the Matter of Henry Caban, Petitioner, v Alexander Chananau et al., Respondents.

Application pursuant to CPLR article 78 in the nature of prohibition unanimously denied, the cross motion granted,- and the petition dismissed, without costs and without disbursements. No opinion. Concur—Stevens, P. J., Markewich, Capozzoli, Lane and Nunez, JJ.
